item.title: CVE-2023-26217|2024-10-24T17:36:09.865Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20ebx%20add-ons
item.description: The Data Exchange Add-on component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons contains an easily exploitable vulnerability that allows a low privileged user with import permissions and network access to the EBX server to execute arbitrary SQL statements on the affected system. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons: versions 4.5.17 and below, versions 5.6.2 and below, version 6.1.0.
